- WOOL Pouch: https://opensea.io/collection/wool-pouch
- Land: https://opensea.io/collection/wolf-game-land
- Farmers: https://opensea.io/collection/wolf-game-farmer

Full-feature game coming in 2022: https://twitter.com/wolfdotgame/status/1462641223005614087

- Discord: https://www.discord.gg/wolfgame
- Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/wolfdotgame

*Your NFTs may accumulate a utility token (“WOOL”) when they are staked in the smart contract. WOOL has no other functionality other than within the Wolf Game ecosystem, and it cannot be purchased from The Wolf Game Developers. The Wolf Game Developers do not provide or intend to provide a secondary marketplace for WOOL.*
